{
  "stem": "6777.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a little shopkeeper who had a cellar under his shop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this Melamed, the cashier, they hidden him there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I visited him there a few times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the one time where I came they told me, go away quickly because he has given himself up to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He couldn't stand anymore living in the hiding all the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I have been told to disappear quickly because they may be under observation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that happened, too, that people did get a good hiding place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they couldn't stand that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But there have been other people who did go out on the cards which I brought in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what is being afraid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I still don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I have been determined that I will make it, absolutely determined that I will make it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just as well as, much later, here, in Australia, I also had some reasons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I still believe I will make it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the final aktion took place in April, I've been that day in the council's building, in the building department.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Germans came in and ordered all, with the exception of a few people, to get out of the building.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I've been among the ones who've been allowed to stay because they needed still some paperwork.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I stood at the window of the first floor, and I've seen a German SS man throwing a grenade into the cellars-- you know, in Warsaw, the houses have been built differently than here.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The multi-story houses had all cellars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people have been bricking over the windows from the cellars and made it-- making it into little bunkers.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
